me/user/cypherclaw-data/samples/` with `library/`, `self/`, `room/`, `contact/`, `theramini/`, `keyboard/` subdirs and `index.sqlite`. | T1 | 6 | 3 | CCS-004 | T-001 | - `SampleLibrary.bootstrap(root)` creates the six subdirectories + `index.sqlite` if missing, idempotent<br/>- documented as the canonical layout in module docstring<br/>- tests verify bootstrap on tmp dir creates all six subdirs and the SQLite file |\n+| 28 | T-028 | Implement `SampleSelector` mood/mode/arc-aware picker with deterministic seed-based selection within match set. | T1 | 3 | 3 | CCS-005 | T-001 | - `SampleSelector(library, rng_seed: int)` exposes `select(mode: ArtistMode, arc_phase: str, mood: Mapping[str,float], target_character: tuple[str,...] = (), avoid_recent: int = 5) -> SampleRecord &#124; None`<br/>- selection prefers samples with matching `arc_phase` and overlapping mood (dot-product over energy/valence/arousal); falls back to character_tags only; falls back to library random within source-source preference per-mode<br/>- `avoid_recent` excludes the N most-recently-played samples (per-mode rolling window)<br/>- per-mode source preference: solitary→[self,contact,room,library]; companion→[library,self,room]; working_ambience→[room,library]; evening_reflection→[self,library,theramini]; storm→[contact,library,room]<br/>- selection is deterministic given (library state, rng_seed, kwargs)<br/>- tests verify per-mode preference order, mood-overlap ranking, avoid_recent, deterministic replay |\n+| 29 | T-029 | Add `sw_sampler` to `SIGNATURE_VOICES` quintet in `artist_identity.py` and update `VOICE_ROLES` so a `\"sampler\"` role maps to `\"sw_sampler\"`. | T1 | 3 | 3 | CCS-006 | T-001 | - `SIGNATURE_VOICES` becomes `(\"sw_bell_warm\", \"sw_bowed\", \"sw_breath\", \"sw_pad\", \"sw_sampler\")`<br/>- `VOICE_ROLES[\"sampler\"] = \"sw_sampler\"`<br/>- existing `VOICE_ROLES` keys for melody/counter/color/texture/bass unchanged<br/>- existing `test_artist_identity.py::TestSignatureVoices::test_